contentrichtext.text: {{Unreferenced stub|auto=yes|date=December 2009}} The '''National Democratic Rally''' (''Rassemblement national dÃ©mocratique'') is a [[political party]] in [[Senegal]]. It is the party of the late [[Cheikh Anta Diop]]. At the [[legislative]] [[elections in Senegal|elections]] on 29 April 2001, the party won 0.7% of the popular vote and 1 out of 120 seats. The party didn't take part in the [[legislative]] [[Senegalese parliamentary election, 2007|elections]] of 3 June 2007. {{Senegalese political parties}} [[Category:Political parties in Senegal]] {{Senegal-party-stub}}
